<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Inventor(s). (Issue date). <em>Patent number</em>. Source.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Inventor">Smith, A.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Issue date">2056</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Patent number">Patent No. 123,456</span></em>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Source">Washington, DC: U.S. Patent and Trademark Office</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
