<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br>
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	U.S. Patent No. 123,456 (2056) provides a new design&hellip;
	<br>
	Alternatively: A recent design (U.S. Patent No. 123,456, 2056) enables&hellip;
</blockquote>
<br>
When the patent is referred to more than once in the same paragraph do not include the date 
in subsequent references, as long as the patent cannot be confused with others cited.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	A recent design, U.S. Patent No. 123,456 (2056) enables&hellip; However, 
	U.S. Patent No. 123,456 does not&hellip;
</blockquote>
